Subject: [PATCH 21/21] =?UTF-8?q?DEBUG:=20probe=20CBUF=20SRAM=20weight=20r?=
 =?UTF-8?q?egion=20(0xe0000/0xf0000)=20vs=20data=20region=20=E2=80=94=20is?=
 =?UTF-8?q?=20the=20CMAC's=20weight=20bank=20staged=3F?=
